{"tid":1299992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「緊急」重大轉捩點黎啦","createTime":"2019-07-09T08:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T09:45:45.000Z","uid":263809,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ed62434548ceafbac1410c38c47bf33b1787e945","tid":1299992,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"長期以黎<br />\n愛國愛黨大本營的連登仔都比一堆藍絲誤會<br />\n但最近人民評分系統終於將所有顏色都weconnect啦<br />\n作為愛國愛黨的藍絲大本營<br />\n一定好多惡習 例如搵唔到廁所 亂拋垃圾 隨處食煙 破壞公物 搭車用小童飛 等等..<br />\n評分系統的黎臨絕對係我地的末日<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣組請盡快宣傳出去</span></span><br />\n<br />\n火燒到大家身上啦<br />\n快啲話比各位家中老人聽呢個普天同慶的消色<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb8e6db5a24ad936543e1fd1ef713bcbf1acd8b6","tid":1299992,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"推上熱門"},{"pid":"03fbf9ccbb09959740897cdc6021aa0f790d819a","tid":1299992,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:32:01.000Z","msg":"大家幫手一齊推比文宣組"},{"pid":"024b190ec945e5771082ea45c1ebba09e5909098","tid":1299992,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:32:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a35172e1b1a56fce576387d71dee7ba4279a92db","tid":1299992,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:32:54.000Z","msg":"愛國愛港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13abb6e1b18d1fc4aff5892db187b3245eec0cf0","tid":1299992,"uid":263809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:33:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fafdd9c6071445938738b08e5